## Installation:

$ git clone git://github.com:soulston/vim-bundle.git ~/.vim
$ mkdir -p .vim/bundle
$ git clone git://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git .vim/bundle

OR on a remote box with no key:

$ git clone https://github.com/soulston/vim-bundle.git ~/.vim
$ mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
$ git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

Create sylinks (REQUIRED for Vundle to run):
$ ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
$ ln -s ~/.vim/.gvimrc ~/.gvimrc (if needed)

Some useful aliases for .bashprofile:

alias ll='ls -la'

Vundle (from vim):
:PluginInstall

